com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures

Class FullPhoto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures.ThumbPhoto
      • com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures.FullPhoto

  • public class FullPhoto
extends ThumbPhoto
    Class that represent full resolution photo and hold all the info of the full resolution photo, hold the: url, height, width, favorites, uploader, category, size, views and others.
